{
  "id": "3-3",
  "title": "Act 3: Let's Escape Together",
  "startNode": "main",
  "nodes": {
    "main": {
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "marker",
          "id": "ch3_act3_start"
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "blackout",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "scanlines",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "This discussion lasted nearly two hours.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Soren's first response was refusal—he wasn't someone who took needless risks.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "And \"venture into the wasteland to visit an enemy nation in search of war's origins\" had costs that far exceeded benefits by any calculation. He laid out his objections one by one, his logic airtight with no gaps.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 900
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Elias",
          "text": "We're already maximum bounty. Stay in the Ark, we'll be found eventually. Go up-levels—we don't have permits, can't access them.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Elias",
          "text": "Going outside is the only path that actually lets us survive.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "He laid the data fragments they'd retrieved from the neural network in front of them.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Elias",
          "text": "And besides—don't you want to know how this war started?",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Soren stared at the data. He said nothing.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Lyra",
          "text": "I want to go.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Her tone was resolute, not impulsive—the voice of someone who'd thought it through.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Lyra",
          "text": "I don't know what we can accomplish, but if we give up before even understanding what happened, nothing will ever change.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Alea sat in the corner, saying nothing. Now all eyes turned to her.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Alea",
          "text": "I have nothing to lose. <delay ms=\"500\"/>Let's go.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Soren ultimately didn't continue objecting.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "He quietly gathered up the maps, then unrolled a larger regional chart. It showed the Ark's outer perimeter and the distribution of shield nodes.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Soren",
          "text": "Then we need three things.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "system",
          "display": {
            "topLeft": "[MISSION REQUIREMENTS]",
            "center": "1. Neural Interface Stabilizers\n2. Basic Medical Supplies\n3. Armed Combat Module",
            "bottomRight": "Source: Military Armory"
          },
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "instant"
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "There won't be sufficient rest time crossing the wasteland for neural sync rates to naturally recover. Without stabilizers as a buffer, soul detachment risk escalates dramatically.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Medical supplies are for basic physical trauma if the body takes damage in the wasteland—anti-inflammatory, hemostatic, radiation countermeasures.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Soren",
          "text": "Wasteland creatures won't show mercy just because you're civilian. Both Mondris and Solmaris have defensive systems along their borders. Going in unarmed is suicide.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Soren",
          "text": "Alpha bodies can mount weapons modules via neural interface, effectively controlling external machinery for combat. But those modules only exist in military inventory.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Elias",
          "text": "So we raid the military armory.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Soren",
          "text": "It's <em>infiltration</em>, not raiding. I need tonight to map the surveillance layout. Tomorrow we move during shift change.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Elias",
          "text": "Understood.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Lyra was already reorganizing their supplies, working with quick, efficient movements. She sorted the unnecessary items to one side and stacked the lightweight essentials in neat piles.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Lyra",
          "text": "Everyone should get some real sleep tonight. After tomorrow, who knows when we'll get that chance again.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Elias",
          "text": "Optimism.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "Lyra",
          "text": "Practicality. Well-rested people work better. That's just sense.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 26
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Alea watched this unfold from her corner without speaking.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She pulled her pack closer and started organizing her own gear.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 2000
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "ms": 1200,
          "args": {
            "stay": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "scanlines",
          "args": {
            "enabled": false
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "end"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "onComplete": [
    "reward",
    "complete"
  ]
}
